89.5	M._Night_Shyamalan	M. Night Shyamalan	Manoj Shyamalan (Maṉōj Śyāmaḷaṉ; born 6 August 1970), known professionally as M. Night Shyamalan, is an Indian-born American screenwriter, film director, and producer known for making movies with contemporary supernatural plots. He is also known for filming his movies (and staging his plots) in and around Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, where he was raised.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/M._Night_Shyamalan_2008_-_still_40580_crop.jpg/220px-M._Night_Shyamalan_2008_-_still_40580_crop.jpg
